duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide medical nutrition therapy to patients in a one-on-one therapy setting and via telehealth.
Collaborate with the team and follow the Sensibly Sprouted Approach (motivational interviewing and advanced methods of MNT).
Participate in continuous education, including quarterly open-door leadership meetings and weekly dietitian roundtables.
Focus on clinical learning, team collaboration, and personal growth.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor's degree in Dietetics or related field (Master's preferred)
